snippet.title: Kingdom Come: Deliverance - The Good, the Bad and the Sneaky
snippet.description:
Welcome to the beautiful countryside of Bohemia 1403. But there is no time to lose as Lord Hanush has sent us on an important quest to investigate the Neuhof stable raid. How will you approach this? Will you settle your mission with the tip of your blade? Your silver-tongue? Or do you rely on your stealth? 

Tell your story on February 13th with Kingdom Come: Deliverance.

Choose your weapon & Pre-Order now!

Collector’s Edition:
